# Cloudflare Workers Assets handles clean URLs automatically:
# /about.html → 307 redirect to /about, and /about serves about.html.
# Don't add /<route> → /<route>.html 200 entries here — they cause loops.

# Legacy Wix URL paths → new clean URLs (301 permanent redirect)
# When mosaicclimbing.com cuts over from Wix to Cloudflare, search-engine
# results, social shares, and old bookmarks for these paths will land on
# the right pages with full SEO credit transferred.
/the-experience    /about        301
/instruction       /booking      301
/details           /about        301
/events            /calendar     301
/youth-classes     /booking      301

# WWW canonicalization — both apex and www serve content identically,
# but search engines prefer one. Pick apex (mosaicclimbing.com) as
# canonical. (Cloudflare also handles this at the domain level once the
# custom domain is wired up; this is a belt-and-suspenders fallback.)
https://www.mosaicclimbing.com/*  https://mosaicclimbing.com/:splat  301!
